# ── graphify corpus exclusions (gitignore syntax) ────────────────────────────
# Read natively by graphify's detect/extract — keeps the knowledge graph free
# of generated, vendored and binary content. Mirror of the manual filter used
# for the initial 2026-06-11 build; the git post-commit hook respects it too.

# Generated / vendored (never knowledge)
node_modules/
Plugin/owismind/resource/owismind-app/
Plugin/ready-for-dataiku/
graphify-out/

# Harness meta-config (not project knowledge)
.claude/

# Binary / image assets (no extractable text knowledge)
docs/screenshots/
*.png
*.svg
*.ico

# Transient debug artifacts (raw DSS trace exports — not knowledge)
salesdrive/*.csv
